Meanwhile, most immigrant workers still live in Russia illegally.
"Welcome or forbidden the passage to strangers"
Many visitors claim that receiving official status in our country is not that easy.
The cause is bureaucratic obstacles and difficulties of the language itself.
Moreover, legalization costs money: from twelve thousand to sixteen thousand roubles.
However, a fake registration can be made quickly and by only one thousand five hundred rubles.
